{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_134","type":"agent_message","text":"The bytecode confirms the crucial path: `ReactiveHttpServiceClientAutoConfiguration` is gated only by `@ConditionalOnClass(WebClientAdapter)` and `@ConditionalOnBean(HttpServiceProxyRegistry.class)`, while `ImportHttpServices` uses `@Import(ImportHttpServiceRegistrar.class)` plus merged-annotation scanning. I’m inspecting the registrar and bean-definition path now to see which metadata is still arriving too late for `OnBeanCondition`."}}
